---
title: One-Pot Mexican Quinoa with Sweet Corn, Avocado, and Feta
description: You won’t be left with a pile of dishes after this easy one-pot meal. We’ve combined quinoa, black beans, diced tomatoes, and corn for a satisfying Mexican-inspired meal. For a touch of richness, creamy avocado and tangy feta finish off the dish.
